EDUCATIONAL PURPOSE NOTICE:

This project is created for educational and learning purposes. It demonstrates:
- Go programming fundamentals
- CLI application development
- HTTP API integration
- JSON data handling
- Caching implementation
- Test-driven development

This project uses the PokeAPI (https://pokeapi.co/) which is a free and open 
Pokemon API. All Pokemon names, images, and data are trademarks of Nintendo, 
Game Freak, and Creatures Inc. This project is not affiliated with or 
endorsed by Nintendo, Game Freak, or Creatures Inc.

